highlights.text: AP Dhillon has the most spots on Top Songs Delhi. Excuses is the highest at #11.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Delhi the longest, at 64 weeks straight.
Kahani Suno 2.0 by Kaifi Khalil is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Delhi, up 25 spots at #69.
KALESHI CHORI by DG IMMORTALS, Raga, Harjas Harjaayi, VIRTUAL_AF, and DARK HORSE is the highest new entry on Top Songs Delhi at #51.
